Sentence: the head of the catholic church in phoenix , arizona , bishop thomas o'brien has resigned. just one day after being charged with a felony. he is accused of leaving the scene of a fatal accident. earlier this month o'brien narrowly escaped prosecution over his handling of sexual abuse allegations against priests .
